    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 420G manual transmission offers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing honest signs of use, the mechanical synchronicity and throttle response remain peak, making this a driver-focused example ready for the twisties.",
