      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of reliability and comfort. The exterior presents beautifully with a high-gloss finish, showing only the most minor signs of regular road use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a remarkably clean cabin where the upholstery remains firm and free of significant wear. Every feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the ice-cold climate control, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent multi-point inspection. It has been driven thoughtfully and maintained without compromise, making it a dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality vehicle that feels and drives like it has many years of life ahead.",
