    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it's been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to go. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home\u2014come see it for yourself and take it for a spin!",
