      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit remains mechanically robust, with the double-VANOS system recently serviced and the rear subframe mounting points inspected and reinforced to mitigate fatigue. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for precise lateral turn-in. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the internal combustion cycle remains efficient with consistent compression across all six cylinders. Recent fluid service includes Liqui Moly 10W-60 and a comprehensive cooling system refresh to manage thermal loads during spirited driving.",
